Description:
The story of Aruba Trading Company is not a short one. In fact, it spans almost 100 years and six generations, dating all the way back to 1923. Our commitment to the beautiful island of Aruba, in other words, began long ago and remains a passion we still hold dear today.

Aruba Trading Company delivers products to more than 600 relations located all over Aruba; companies, supermarkets, restaurants, hotels and private clients. We value each and every one of our clients and work hard to maintain a high level of trust using the same values as almost 100 years ago.

OUR VALUES
At Aruba Trading Company our values are both simple and incredibly important:

Respect for the island and our customers alike;
Total devotion to Aruba and our clients;
Maintaining and exceeding the highest ethical standards in the industry;
Ensuring operational excellence.

As a wholesaler, we work hard to provide premium brands and products to our customers while maintaining a high level of trust. We embrace innovation and see challenges as opportunities.

We are passionate about our work, our customers, and our team. We cherish the relationships we have with our suppliers and the brands they send our way and we hold ourselves to the highest standards of professionalism and integrity.

A wholesale and retail trade company that imports high-quality and delicious products from various countries around the world. We work directly with winemakers and producers from Italy, France, Spain, Portugal, South Africa and other countries. We are looking for new flavors and bringing them to Lithuania.
We work in several ways:
- distribution in the HoReCa channel;
- boutique-style wine and gourmet product stores;
- online shop www.winemaker.lt;
- tastings and wine education.
